    <item>
      <title>苏纳克遭遇双重民意调查打击，工作年龄选民抛弃保守党</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/rishi-sunak-hit-by-fresh-poll-blows-as-working-age-voters-desert-tories</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一项新的民意调查显示，英国劳动年龄选民已不再支持执政的保守党，该民意调查突显了首相里希·苏纳克(Rishi Sunak)在试图防止在未来九个月的大选中遭遇压倒性失败时所面临的挑战。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/rishi-sunak-hit-by-fresh-poll-blows-as-working-age-voters-desert-tories</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 12:08:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
