    <item>
      <title>分析发现，没有证据表明英国央行的决定受到选举的影响</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/no-evidence-boe-decisions-swayed-by-elections-analysis-finds</link>
      <description><![CDATA[最新分析显示，英国央行可能在下一次英国大选前两次降息，该分析发现政治时间表并未影响央行过去的决定。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/no-evidence-boe-decisions-swayed-by-elections-analysis-finds</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 10:07:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
